Class Auth

java.lang.Object
  com.fewstera.injectablemedicinesguide.Auth

public class Auth
extends java.lang.Object

Class for handling authentication This class is used for validating user credentials with the NHS server. This class is also used for saving, retrieving and deleting users credentials.

Since:
1.0
Author:
Aidan Wynne Fewster
